      <h1 class='title'>UK Trade and Investment Website</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1728WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1728ws' title='Col. 1728WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1728WS' name='column_1728ws' href='#column_1728ws' rel='bookmark'>1728WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_455'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-james-arbuthnot' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_455' title='Link to this speech by Mr James Arbuthnot' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-james-arbuthnot" title="Mr James Arbuthnot">Mr. Arbuthnot</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry what plans she has to introduce<span class="italic">(a)</span> new and <span class="italic">(b)</span> increased charges for information, advice or assistance obtained by British businesses through the website of UK Trade and Investment. [189317]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_456'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-douglas-alexander' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_456' title='Link to this speech by Mr Douglas Alexander' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-douglas-alexander" title="Mr Douglas Alexander">Mr. Alexander</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Arising from the Spending Review 2004 settlement, UK Trade and Investment are seeking to achieve efficiency gains through consideration of greater cost recovery for its services. Officials are considering options on how best to achieve this.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
